snippet.title: Dread Hunger - Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
Dread Hunger on Steam: https://bit.ly/3a8wraC

Dread Hunger is an eight player game of survival and betrayal. Explorers path their ship through the unforgiving Arctic. Among the crew, two traitors call on dark powers to undermine them.

Follow the socials for news and updates!

Discord: https://discord.gg/ZM8RRHy95w
Twitter: https://twitter.com/DreadHungerGame
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/DreadHunger

#DreadHunger #gaming #trailer
